caption.p: Cyclic voltammetry curves of the NCO-5/1 sample. ( a) 1, 9 and 200 cycles, ( b) example of deconvolution of the cyclic voltammetry (CV) curve of the NCO-5/1 sample, ( c) anode CV curves of the films before, ( d) after cycling (after 200 cycles) related to the thickness of the substrate. Presented curves for ( c, d) plotted in the same coordinate system but physically spaced.
